      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "On October 16, 1950, at approximately 2:55 P.M., Trooper Isabell stopped us at this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "Installation and showed us an object in the north that was traveling toward the northw",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "It looked to be about 2,000 feet in the air and a white-silverish looking color, rotat",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "in a counter clockwise manner. It was round in shape and going in a rather fast motio",
      "status": "pending_image_audit"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "This object was at a high altitude and seemed to come in sight and then disappear. It",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
